<div class="contactbackground">
  <div class="contactbanner pt-4 mb-4">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="pt-3">Welcome Lets see what i can do for you</h1>
      <h2>You've reached an impressive milestone. Let's continue the journey with a complimentary chat. Kindly complete the form, and I'll be sure to reach out promptly</h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container pt-4 mt-4 pb-4">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <p>Please complete the form and we will get in contact so you can ask us any questions you might have.</p>
        <p>I look forward to hearing from you and about your business.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="contactform col-sm-6">
        <%= form_for @contact_form do |f| %>
          <div class="form-group">
            <%= f.label :name %>
            <%= f.text_field :name, class: 'form-control' %>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <%= f.label :email %>
            <%= f.email_field :email, class: 'form-control' %>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <%= f.label :message %>
            <%= f.text_area :message, class: 'form-control' %>
          </div>
          <%= f.submit 'Send', class: 'mt-2 btn btn-dark' %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>
